WEBVTT

00:01:26.927 --> 00:01:30.373
the design and the creation
of spaces between buildings,

00:01:30.397 --> 00:01:31.561
the landscape.

00:01:31.585 --> 00:01:33.603
It's man's interaction with the landscape.

00:01:33.627 --> 00:01:36.001
Our construction
of the built environment --

00:01:36.025 --> 00:01:39.327
that's what I mean by architecture.

00:01:39.998 --> 00:01:42.023
It's not a specialized thing.

00:01:43.060 --> 00:01:46.016
And over the last, I suppose,
20 or 30 years,

00:01:46.040 --> 00:01:49.356
with the predominance of the internet

00:01:49.380 --> 00:01:52.527
and the wonderful
and exciting advancements

00:01:52.551 --> 00:01:54.338
that are taking place in technology,

00:01:54.362 --> 00:01:57.963
one of the things that has happened
is that our perception of the world

00:01:57.987 --> 00:01:59.377
has become commodified.

00:01:59.401 --> 00:02:01.571
It's become reduced in many ways